A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Vehicle Laws – Drivers’ Schools and Driver Education Programs – Age of
3 Instruction Vehicles
4 FOR the purpose of prohibiting a vehicle that is older than a certain number of model years
5 from being used for instruction in a drivers’ school or a driver education program;
6 and generally relating to drivers’ schools and driver education programs.
